Title: Magnetic monopoles with generalized quantization condition
Authors: Alexander I Nesterov and F. Aceves de la Cruz
Comments: REVTEX4 file, 6 pages. To appear in Physics Letters A
Subj-class: High Energy Physics - Theory; Mathematical Physics
Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. A302 (2002) 253-260
\\
  Theory of pointlike magnetic monopole with an arbitrary magnetic charge is
considered. It is shown that a proper description requires making use of
nonunitary representations of the rotation group and the nonassociative
generalization of the gauge group and fibre bundle theory.
